    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><em>Unsung heroes, untold stories. So much time outdoors, so little time to write about them.</em> <strong>These are the Untold Trip Reports.</strong></p>

<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/hendrikmorkel/9537611324/" title="Dusk by HendrikMorkel, on Flickr"><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7312/9537611324_1787dd85ec_b.jpg" width="1024" height="680" alt="Dusk" /></a></p>

